                </p>
            </div>
            

            <div class="mb-4">
                <h5>
                    Our Poke-mission
                </h5>
                
                <p>
                    At Pokemon Collection, we're on a quest to make Pokemon card collecting as fun and exciting as a wild encounter with a shiny Charizard! 
                    Here's what we're all about:
                    <ul>
                        <li class="my-3">
                            <strong> Poke-passion</strong><br> We're obsessed with Pokemon cards, and we want to share that passion with you! Whether you are a new collector or seaoned veteran, we're here to help you on your pokemon journey.
                        </li>
                        <li class="my-3">
                            <strong> Creative Collections </strong><br> Create and manage your collections, whether it be cards you aspire to get, cards you want to trade or simply to build your dream Pokemon line up.
                        </li>
                        <li class="my-3">
                            <strong> The Complete Pokedex</strong><br> Like the pokedex our database is ever expanding and evolving as we discover new species and variants. Help us grow and reach our goal of being the most comprehensive Pokemon card database on the web.
                        </li>
                    </ul>           
                </p>

            </div>

            
            <div>
